headline: TXT's Arm Delivers First Aeromedical Aircraft to Peruvian Air Force
summary: Textron's unit, Textron Aviation, announces the delivery of its first multi-mission Beechcraft King Air 360CHW aircraft to the Peruvian Air Force.
